    "description": {
      "value": "<p><strong>Scroll of Remove Curse</strong> (Level 3 Abjuration)</p><p>At your touch, all curses affecting one creature or object end. If the object is a cursed magic item, its curse remains, but the spell breaks its owner's attunement to the object so it can be removed or discarded.</p><p><strong>Components:</strong> V, S</p><p><strong>Casting Time:</strong> 1 action | <strong>Range:</strong> Touch | <strong>Duration:</strong> Instantaneous</p><p><em>Classes: Cleric, Paladin, Warlock, Wizard</em></p>",
